channel.title: Client Compiling Problem
channel.description:
Hello,
I'm new to a lot of this and I have a problem when I compile the client.
Yes, I am aware that there is a section above about all Compling questions, but I've gone through numerous pages and haven't found my problem.
Well, when I compile my client it says,
'The system cannot find the path specified Press any key to continue...'
Yes, I know that their is a code that you copy and paste in the edit part of the Compiler, but I have no idea what that code is!
- Ive tried the codes in the section above ( they dont work )
Thanks for your help and cooperation!
~ Bunny Ears
